### =============================================
### Multi-tenant SaaS API - HTTP Collection
### =============================================
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### or convert to curl/HTTPie as needed
### =============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
@tenantId = YOUR_TENANT_UUID_HERE

### ===== AUTH =====

### Register a new user (public - no tenant needed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "StrongP@ss123"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "StrongP@ss123"
}

###

### Refresh access token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ===== TENANTS (SUPER_ADMIN only) =====

### Create a new tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corporation",
  "subdomain": "acme",
  "plan": "free"
}

###

### List all tenants (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get tenant by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Update tenant
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "pro",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Delete tenant (also drops the schema)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ===== USERS =====

### Create user in a tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "jane@acme.com",
  "password": "SecureP@ss456",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

###

### List users (filtered by tenant for non-SUPER_ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

###

### Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

###

### Update user
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane Updated",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}

###

### Delete user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

###

### ===== BILLING (Stripe) =====

### Create Stripe customer for tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/billing/customers/{{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create subscription (assign plan)
POST {{baseUrl}}/billing/subscriptions/{{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "pro"
}

###

### Cancel subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/billing/subscriptions/{{tenantId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get billing portal URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/billing/portal/{{tenantId}}?returnUrl=http://localhost:3000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Stripe webhook (call from Stripe CLI in test mode)
### stripe trigger invoice.paid
POST {{baseUrl}}/billing/webhook
stripe-signature: whsec_test_signature
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### ===== PLANS =====

### List available plans (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/plans?page=1&limit=10

###

### Get plan details (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/plans/PLAN_UUID_HERE

###

### Create a plan (SUPER_ADMIN only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pro",
  "price": 29.99,
  "maxUsers": 50,
  "features": ["unlimited_projects", "priority_support", "api_access"],
  "stripePriceId": "price_pro_monthly_test"
}

###

### Update a plan
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/plans/PLAN_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 39.99,
  "maxUsers": 100
}

###

### Delete a plan
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/plans/PLAN_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
